node.text:
I don’t know 🤷🏿‍♂️, how you’re going to absorb this message, but please I need y’all to understand : I won’t be doing any bodybuilding competition throughout the year 2020. I need some time to bring up my size and muscle density .
.
.

I’m sorry to everyone who really wanted me to compete again next year. This decision was made by myself and my mum , after I Placed 4th twice 🎖🎖this year.
.
.
.
I’m still grateful to God , my mum , @bodymoney , @ifesfitworld , @naziftm16 and @ruff_diesel  for your support and motivation. God bless you all abundantly. Amen 🙏🏿. Till 2021 it’s OFFICIAL GROWTH OFF SEASON.

node.text:
MONDAY MOTIVATION: If you want to do something, be passionate about it, then be willing to put in everything to make sure it works , that way if you’re not giving it 100% , you will know what’s lagging. 

BREAKING INFORMATION: I won’t be doing any bodybuilding competition this year sadly, In order to focus and finalize getting my BSc Certificate as a medical lab scientist. I apologize to my support team and people who wanted to see my comeback on stage this year, I tried everything within my power to make sure I would compete but sadly the academic struggle stretched me an extra time, I pray that I scale through this last phase effortlessly and move a comeback worth remembering next year. 

I Personally apologize to my big brothers to kindly understand and I wish them well in their competitions this year ❤️🙏🏾 …. @ruff_diesel @amouzoucaleb @bodymoney_fit and @franklyn_la_promesse 

GOD IS GOOD 😊 ❤️

node.text:
My man crush every day, every moment, you’re amazing and such a wonderful soul 😊❤️. 
Appreciate your struggles, your days of greatness has only just began, thank you for staying strong, thank you for learning everything you know on your own , thank you for forgiving people who wronged us even tho you don’t forget, Thank you for shouldering our depression, heart breaks , pain and insecurities and thank you celebrating all our past wins, birthdays and set ups. 

I will continue to respect you, love you and follow your goals 🙂❤️. 
Damn you sexy chocolate boo thang 😊❤️, you deserve the hype and appreciate. 

God bless your crypto business, media marketing hustle, your family and loved ones.
